#text=It was in last spring , when we were taking photos by standing in front of our house , we felt like our photos lacked something .
#text=Later we reached a conclusion that we do n't have enough green around our house .
#text=So we thought it would be nice if we plant a tree in our yard .
#text=So we started our search on trees .
#text=During summer time a lot of rabbits come to our house and destroy all plants .
#text=Therefore we are in need of a plant that should n't attract rabbits .
#text=We read reviews of different types of trees .
#text=At last we reached a conclusion to buy a maple tree so that we can enjoy fall too .
#text=We were new to planting a tree , so we watched some videos to get some information .
#text=In one website they suggested to plant a somewhat tall plant rather than a small plant .
#text=So we went to Home Depot bought a plant and a shovel .
#text=It was a very beautiful maple tree .
#text=After reaching home I dug a pit just to fit the plant base which was packed with some soil .
#text=Me and my wife held it and kept the plant in to the pit and removed the plastic sheets which wrapped the plant base together with the soil .
#text=After that we poured the soil back to the pit and made the plant to stand straight .
